So the more humans, the more brains that we can have kind of working on these problems

00:08:12.959 --> 00:08:16.399
and the technologies are more accessible, I think that that's fantastic.

00:08:16.399 --> 00:08:24.079
So I very much see R and RStudio and Posit as very much in that, like for that.

00:08:24.079 --> 00:08:30.320
And then when I joined Databricks, I learned that the founders initially, when they invented

00:08:30.320 --> 00:08:33.919
Spark, which is the main technology that Databricks kind of got started with, it's kind of a long

00:08:33.919 --> 00:08:34.919
