00:08:34.919 --> 00:08:37.359
But when they invented it, they wanted to give it away.

00:08:37.359 --> 00:08:41.320
They did make it open source, but they were like going to these different companies and

00:08:41.320 --> 00:08:46.359
they were trying to just say, hey, use this awesome technology.

00:08:46.359 --> 00:08:50.960
And the companies kind of pushed them back and were like, hey, well, there's no nice

00:08:50.960 --> 00:08:54.919
science project you have here, but there's no enterprise support, there's no adoption

00:08:54.919 --> 00:08:57.080
of this, there's too much risk.

00:08:57.080 --> 00:09:01.239
