00:09:01.239 --> 00:09:02.580
on top of it.

00:09:02.580 --> 00:09:08.359
But the spirit of that was definitely, we want to democratize the power of big data

00:09:08.359 --> 00:09:12.559
and these technologies so that people can work on really, really difficult problems

00:09:12.559 --> 00:09:16.239
and not be limited by the amount of data that they can process.

00:09:16.239 --> 00:09:21.400
So I think that those kind of, the two companies I think actually work really well together

00:09:21.400 --> 00:09:27.320
