00:49:39.780 --> 00:49:41.780
So it's all the same information.

00:49:41.780 --> 00:49:43.780
At the end of the day, it's the same data point.

00:49:43.780 --> 00:49:47.780
It's an observation of January 1st, 2015, but somebody, you know, you could

00:49:47.780 --> 00:49:55.780
have literally January 1st, 2015, or you could have 0, 1, 0, 1, 2015.

